<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Subscribe to Our Newsletter</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background: #f0f4f8;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        .header {
            background: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.5em;
        }
        .container {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .section h2 {
            font-size: 2em;
            color: #1F316F;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #1F316F;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .section p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .form-group input[type="email"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #ced4da;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            font-size: 16px;
            box-shadow: inset 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: border-color 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
        }
        .form-group input[type="email"]:focus {
            border-color: #1F316F;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.25);
            outline: none;
        }
        .btn-submit {
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background-color: #1F316F;
            border: none;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
        }
        .btn-submit:hover {
            background-color: #1F316F;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .footer {
            background: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 0;
        }
        li{
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Subscribe to Our Newsletter</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="section">
            <h2>Stay Updated with Our Latest News</h2>
            <p>Subscribe to our newsletter to receive updates on the latest trends, offers, and news directly to your inbox. Stay ahead with exclusive content and special offers just for our subscribers!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Sign Up</h2>
            <form action="/subscribe" method="post" novalidate>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="email">Email Address</label>
                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Enter your email" required>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">Subscribe</button>
            </form>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Why Subscribe?</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><i class="fas fa-star"></i> Exclusive Offers: Be the first to know about our exclusive promotions and discounts.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i> Latest Updates: Receive updates on our latest products and services.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Insights & Tips: Get valuable tips and insights to make the most out of our offerings.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Ghar. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
